    "Id": "chassisdef_fire_wasp_FS9-WSP",
    "Name": "Fire Wasp",
    "Details": "The FS9-WSP is a Star League era hybrid of the Firestarter and Wasp, combining the best traits of both into a single highly mobile 40-ton frame. Six jump jets and MASC push it to 129 kph in bursts while four Flamers make it genuinely dangerous to infantry and heat-sensitive targets. Twin Medium Lasers and a Streak SRM 2 handle direct combat when needed, making it considerably more capable in a straight fight than either of its predecessors.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Narrow/Low Profile</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1</color></b>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_firewasp"
