  "StockRole": "Scout",
  "YangsThoughts": "The SLDF wanted a Firestarter and Wasp rolled into one and Argile Technologies delivered. Only a few dozen were ever built before the Amaris Civil War shut production down, and the ones that survived went with Kerensky into exile. Finding one of these in working condition is genuinely remarkable. It is fast, it jumps well, it burns things, and unlike the originals it can actually hold its own in a firefight if it has to. Treat it carefully.",
